@startuml domain_class
' ============================================================
' HRS 概念クラス図（演習1 / ドメイン分析）
' Issue: [Domain] 概念クラス図を作成する
'
' 方針:
'   - ここには「ホテル業務に存在する概念」だけを置く
'   - Controller / UI / Repository / DB などの実装クラスは入れない
'   - 多重度・ロール名・集約を明示する
' プレビュー: VS Code の PlantUML 拡張（Alt+D）か
'            https://www.plantuml.com/plantuml にコード貼り付け
' ============================================================

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

class Customer {
  customerId
  name
  phone
  email
}

class Staff {
  staffId
  name
}

class Hotel {
  hotelId
  name
}

class Room {
  roomNumber
  status
}

class RoomType {
  typeId
  name
  capacity
  pricePerNight
}

class Reservation {
  reservationId
  checkInDate
  checkOutDate
  status
  createdAt
}

class Stay {
  stayId
  actualCheckInAt
  actualCheckOutAt
}

class Invoice {
  invoiceId
  totalAmount
  issuedAt
}

class Payment {
  paymentId
  amount
  method
  paidAt
}

' --- 状態は列挙として表現（採用するか要判断: docs/01_domain_analysis.md 参照）---
enum ReservationStatus {
  RESERVED
  CANCELLED
  CHECKED_IN
  CHECKED_OUT
}

enum RoomStatus {
  AVAILABLE
  OCCUPIED
  OUT_OF_SERVICE
}

' ============================================================
' 関係と多重度
' ============================================================
Hotel        "1"    o-- "*"    Room                  : owns
RoomType     "1"    --  "*"    Room
Customer     "1"    --  "*"    Reservation
Reservation  "*"    --  "1"    RoomType
Reservation  "0..1" --  "0..1" Room                  : assigned room
Reservation  "1"    --  "0..1" Stay
Stay         "1"    --  "0..1" Invoice
Invoice      "1"    --  "0..1" Payment
Staff        "*"    --  "*"    Stay                  : handles

' 状態の対応（列挙を採用する場合のみ）
Reservation  ..>  ReservationStatus
Room         ..>  RoomStatus

@enduml
